data.description: Unearth a gem in the heart of Bermuda Dunes Country Club with this ideal project for fixers, flippers, or landlords. This unique opportunity features the possibility of a loan takeover subject to existing financing, boasting low payments at an attractive 2.7% interest rate. Perfect for investors or new homebuyers looking for sweat equity combined with beneficial financing terms.Be first to lock up approximately 2,400 square feet of functional floor space on a large, expansive lot. The property has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, including a main structure housing 2 beds and 2 baths, complemented by a casita add-on with 2 additional bedrooms and 1 full bath. Easily add a thrid bedroom to the main house.  This configuration makes it a highly desirable rental property with excellent cash flow potential.Situated in the prestigious Bermuda Dunes Country Club area, this property is not just a home, but a potential cornerstone in a rental portfolio or a unique renovation project. It offers the flexibility to customize for equity growth, rental income, or even as your personal desert retreat, in one of the most desired gold country clubs in the Coachella Valley with among the lowest HOA dues.Please note, the casita add-on square footage, bedrooms, and bath are not reflected in the tax assessor's property profile.
